headline: A Fresh Look at Intercontinental Exchange (ICE) Valuation Following $2B Polymarket Investment and DeFi Expansion
summary: Intercontinental Exchange (ICE) is making waves with its plan to invest up to $2 billion in Polymarket, a major player in the prediction market space. The move highlights ICE’s growing focus on data-driven products and decentralized finance. See our latest analysis for Intercontinental Exchange. The Polymarket investment adds to a string of bold moves for Intercontinental Exchange. This comes just after fresh record volumes in energy and financial futures, along with new climate risk...
